{"tid":752390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"城大有演講廳小型天花倒塌","createTime":"2018-07-22T18:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T10:40:03.000Z","uid":5195,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"555eaf821c0f86ea9a6fb766fd0c5ff14ea3df9c","tid":752390,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T18:26:37.000Z","msg":"2016年5月，城市大學運動中心發生塌天花事件，事隔兩年之後，一個來自城大學生會動漫同人誌幹事會的通告，揭露了城大又有地方冧天花。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁「城大冬祭」發出相關公告，動漫同人誌幹事會收到校方通知，稱由於用作秋祭主舞台之健絡通演講廳（LT-401）日前發生小型天花倒塌事故，為確保使用者安全需要進行全面檢查。<br />\n<br />\n通知指，由於安排及檢查需時，加上視檢查結果或需進行維修工程，故有機會未能於原定城大秋祭之日期，亦即今年11月3日及11月4日借出場地作該會活動之用。"},{"pid":"76fdf78da4f936f4172e566360fdd50f39c1a4aa","tid":752390,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T18:29:43.000Z","msg":"幾時成間嘢塌晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ff572fff79ee0cc04a7c49080ae36ab0b8eb45","tid":752390,"uid":76470,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T18:31:43.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲有錢佬捐個啲錢去晒邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d335a63db781a1d6a4c6b958c2ae28c186d34cb2","tid":752390,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T18:32:42.000Z","msg":"圖"},{"pid":"9396818aa7b22db0f74f4333ab27c9e904ed4804","tid":752390,"uid":78143,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T18:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/023250_b873ddd1a83d0891859c63612ca11a92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F023250_b873ddd1a83d0891859c63612ca11a92.jpg&h=ebed77d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41e3dd121ff8292798c89021b0ee3978155677df","tid":752390,"uid":164167,"l